 on it think about putting the ablitiy for rogues to pick pocket, and enchanters to charm back in the game.  I personally think pick pocket would be great on this server, and a good enchanter friend of mine told me the reason charm was taken out of pvp was to keep people from causing exp deaths.  Now that exp deaths are gonna happen what's your opinion?  BTW try and not turn this into a rant about confirmed rules and how unfair they are...thats why Safehouse has a rant hall.<br>
<br>
Zoggy <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=cylant>Cylant</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/23/01 5:42:50 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Charming and Pickpocket on new PVP Server?</span><hr size=1> Pickpocket - yes... but severly nerfed... it would be fine<br>
Charm - ..yes and no.  It would be fun, but exploited. <p><table width="300">
