</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uiamwotan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>I am Wotan</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.thegamevine.com/~Wotan_Rogue/yinyang.gif border=0 BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/23/01 9:47:59 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.thegamevine.com/~Wotan_Rogue/mask2a.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Charming and Pickpocket on new PVP Server?</span><hr size=1> No all levels!  Think about it. I wanna go pickpocket a lvl 60 with my lvl 20, and run like hell when I fail. <br>
<br>
Level limit is unnecessary, cause if your mark is higher, he can toast you, if lower, well you could toast him and take his coppers anyways.<br>
<br>
