<br>
<br>
Zoggy<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=elegance>Elegance</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/24/01 3:19:46 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Charming and Pickpocket on new PVP Server?</span><hr size=1> &quot;How do we let the Dev team working on the new server know our feelings about these skills?&quot;<br>
<br>
<br>
easy we pay their crack dealers to slip them a message on their next buy. <p>Diabalein Avidya <br>
 Practicing Proctologist for 33 Lvls Of Pure Anal Probing Fun<br>161 Points of Loving, Hand Delivered on the End of a Sharp Stick</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uzoggynog.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zoggynog</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/24/01 3:59:26 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Charming and Pickpocket on new PVP Server?</span><hr size=1> If only I knew their dealers....Besides crack, anyone have a good idea? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/upeyth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Peyth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/24/01 4:16:48 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Charming and Pickpocket on new PVP Server?</span><hr size=1> You can kill anybody whether +/- 5 levels or not. However, you can't loot people out of that range.  So, on that same note, you should not be able to pickpocket people outside of the +/- 5 level range.  In the end tho, I doubt they'll have pvp pickpocket in. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uzoggynog.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zoggynog</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/24/01 4:23:21 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Charming and Pickpocket on new PVP Server?</span><hr size=1> Thats why im askin how we attempt to get Pickpocket, charm, and fear back in.  I know it wont be in unless people ask for it, and ive seen the Safehouse community do amazing things through these message boards.  Thus, I am asking what is the best route to take in order to at least see how the devs feel about this possiblity.  Ive heard Kendrik (sp) is an insider at VI, any chance he could help?  Im hoping someone may have a suggestion on how to accomplish this goal.<br>
<br>
Zoggy <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showMessage?topicID=284.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showMessage?topicID=267.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.emailToFriend?topicID=274.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.threadControl?topicID=274.topic><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/closeThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=274.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=274.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion">Main Lounge<option value="thesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc">News Bulletin<option value="thesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies">Training Studio<option value="thesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers">The Back Alley<option value="thesafehousefrm13">Quests of Norrath<option value="thesafehousetherootcellar">The Root Cellar<option value="thesafehouselaboratory">Laboratory<option value="thesafehousefrm15">The Arena<option value="thesafehousefrm17">Anarchy's Grip<opti